sequenceDiagram
  participant Issuer
  participant Verifier
  participant Pod as SolidPod
  participant Chain as DIDRegistry

  Issuer->>Pod: publish DID document
  Issuer->>Chain: register DID with doc hash
  Issuer->>Pod: publish verifiable credential
  Issuer->>Chain: anchor credential hash with subject DID

  Verifier->>Chain: get DID
  Chain-->>Verifier: controller, doc hash
  Verifier->>Pod: fetch DID document
  Verifier->>Pod: fetch verifiable credential
  Verifier->>Chain: read vc anchor by hash
  Chain-->>Verifier: anchor data